High-quality recruitment is the key to your company's success. 
Here are some fundamental principles:

• A well-crafted and honest job posting; 
• A clear understanding of the candidate you are looking for; 
• The interviewer's skill in accurately and fairly assessing the candidate's key indicators;
• A well-structured hiring process - involving stakeholders, the number of stages, and appropriately adapted test assignments;
• Competitive salary;
• Healthy working conditions.


